CAPTION "選擇需要註冊的檔案類型"
STYLE WS_POPUP|WS_VISIBLE|WS_CAPTION|WS_SYSMENU|DS_CENTER|DS_MODALFRAME|DS_SHELLFONT|DS_3DLOOK
FONT 8, "MS Shell Dlg", 0, 0, 0x1
